summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. W-11, for the improvement of California Avenue, from the intersection of South Street to the intersection of Ninth Avenue, by opening, clearing, grubbing and grading and parking the same, under Ordinance No. 190 the former City of West Seattle and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
